      "y": 0.46631205673758847,
      "rationale_cn": "最高单项分支。90分钟打平后的主要入口是1-1、0-0和2-2，其中0-0与1-1入口都会强化淘汰赛加时的风险控制；若105分钟仍平，双方点球思维增强，挪威虽有定位球和高点优势，但不会无条件持续压上，科特迪瓦也有足够防守结构把比赛拖入点球。",
      "rationale_en": "The highest single branch. The main extra-time entries after a 90-minute draw are 1-1, 0-0 and 2-2; 0-0 and 1-1 both reinforce knockout risk control in extra time. If it is still level after 105 minutes, both sides become more penalty-aware. Norway has set-piece and aerial advantages, but will not press recklessly without limit, and Ivory Coast has enough defensive structure to drag the match to penalties."
    },
    {
      "increment": "1-0",
      "score": "1-0",
      "extra_goals_a": 1,
      "extra_goals_b": 0,
      "conditional_probability": 0.1843971631205675,
      "joint_probability": 0.05,
      "extra_time_outcome": "team_a",
      "category": "extra_time_resolution",
      "deviation_score": 0.33999999999999997,
      "x": 0.33999999999999997,
      "y": 0.1843971631205675,
      "rationale_cn": "挪威加时取胜的主路径。末轮大轮换、Haaland/Sørloth高点、Ødegaard组织、传中、角球、前场任意球和二点球，使挪威在90-105分钟拥有小幅主动权；但科特迪瓦低位紧凑和身体对抗限制其不能被上调到强优势。",
      "rationale_en": "Norway’s main extra-time win path. Heavy rotation in the final group match, Haaland/Sørloth as aerial targets, Ødegaard’s creation, crosses, corners, attacking free kicks and second balls give Norway a small initiative from 90 to 105 minutes. Ivory Coast’s compact low block and physicality prevent this from becoming a strong advantage."
    },
    {
      "increment": "0-1",
      "score": "0-1",
      "extra_goals_a": 0,
      "extra_goals_b": 1,
      "conditional_probability": 0.16666666666666677,
      "joint_probability": 0.04519230769230769,
      "extra_time_outcome": "team_b",
      "category": "extra_time_resolution",
      "deviation_score": 0.33999999999999997,
      "x": 0.33999999999999997,
      "y": 0.16666666666666677,
      "rationale_cn": "科特迪瓦加时取胜的主要反制路径。若挪威为避免点球而边后卫前提，科特迪瓦可通过Amad、Pépé、Yan Diomande等速度点打边路转换或身后空间；该路径真实存在，但依赖速度点留场、体能和第一脚转换质量。",
      "rationale_en": "Ivory Coast’s main extra-time counter-path. If Norway pushes its fullbacks higher to avoid penalties, Ivory Coast can attack wide transitions and space behind through pace outlets such as Amad, Pépé and Yan Diomande. The path is real, but depends on those pace threats staying on, fitness, and the quality of the first transition pass."
    },
    {
      "increment": "2-0",
      "score": "2-0",
      "extra_goals_a": 2,
      "extra_goals_b": 0,
      "conditional_probability": 0.06205673758865254,
      "joint_probability": 0.01682692307692308,
      "extra_time_outcome": "team_a",
      "category": "extra_time_breakout",
      "deviation_score": 0.74,
      "x": 0.74,
      "y": 0.06205673758865254,
      "rationale_cn": "挪威两球加时胜的低概率尾部。需要挪威先通过定位球、传中或禁区混战破局，随后科特迪瓦压出留下第二球空间；更可能发生在2-2、3-3等开放入口或科特迪瓦后场体能崩盘时。",
      "rationale_en": "A low-probability two-goal extra-time win for Norway. It requires Norway to break through first via a set piece, cross or box scramble, after which Ivory Coast pushes up and leaves space for a second goal. It is more likely from open entries such as 2-2 or 3-3, or if Ivory Coast’s back line fades physically."
    },
    {
      "increment": "1-1",
      "score": "1-1",
      "extra_goals_a": 1,
      "extra_goals_b": 1,
      "conditional_probability": 0.04787234042553195,
      "joint_probability": 0.012980769230769231,
      "extra_time_outcome": "draw",
      "category": "penalty_entry",
      "deviation_score": 0.3,
      "x": 0.3,
      "y": 0.04787234042553195,
      "rationale_cn": "加时双方各进一球后仍平，主要来自90分钟2-2或更高比分的开放入口，或加时早段一方先进球后另一方被迫提速。它高于一般多球尾部，但仍明显低于0-0、1-0和0-1，因为淘汰赛加时后段通常降风险。",
      "rationale_en": "Both teams score once in extra time and it remains level, mainly from open 90-minute entries at 2-2 or higher, or when one side scores early in extra time and the other is forced to raise the tempo. It is higher than a typical high-goal tail, but still clearly below 0-0, 1-0, and 0-1 because knockout extra time usually becomes more risk-averse late on."
    },
    {
