      "y": 0.03014184397163123,
      "rationale_cn": "科特迪瓦两球加时胜属于尾部。需要先由边路转换、定位球二点或挪威失误取得领先，再在挪威全线压上时打出第二次反击；其机制存在，但受限于加时整体低节奏和科特迪瓦未必主动冒险。",
      "rationale_en": "A two-goal extra-time win for Ivory Coast is a tail outcome. It requires Ivory Coast to lead first through a wide transition, a set-piece second ball or a Norway error, then strike again as Norway pushes up. The mechanism exists, but is limited by the overall low tempo of extra time and by the fact that Ivory Coast may not proactively take risks."
